Data Extractor Schema

Data Exporter Schema

This document describes the Turbonomic Data Exporter.

The Turbonomic platform includes a Data Exporter component that you can choose to enable when you install the platform. The Data Exporter streams Turbonomic data to a standard format. You can then load that data into search and analytics services such as Elasticsearch.

With the Data Exporter you can build custom tracking of changes to your environment, and follow the details as Turbonomic keeps your applications healthy.

For general information information about Turbonomic, see the full Turbonomic documentation HERE.
